00:17:51.390 --> 00:17:55.290
without disappointing anyone,
so keeping the surprise

00:17:55.290 --> 00:17:59.790
element, the idea that something
is a little bit challenging

00:17:59.790 --> 00:18:02.000
but, at the same
time, also comforting,

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:04.200
which has always been
at the top of my agenda.

00:18:04.200 --> 00:18:07.399
So to make an Ottolenghi
recipe, which is funny

00:18:07.399 --> 00:18:08.940
that I say that--
that's my surname--

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:13.590
but I get that there is
something beyond that.

00:18:13.590 --> 00:18:15.151
It's got a life of its own now.

00:18:15.151 --> 00:18:16.150
SPEAKER 2: It's a brand.

